      <h2>The Division</h2>
      <h3>The Divison is a game taht takes place in modern NewYork City. To be more specific, Manhattan.A virus of small poxs has broken out by a man named Gordon Amherst. The virus was spread through bank notes on black friday. The day millions of dollars are exchnaged. And Manhattan being a city full of unsanitary people, the disease spreads quickly. As people dies, the city goes into complete chaos. The street becomes full of rioters and the sick. The military steps in and creates a quarantine zone now called the Dark Zone. The virus got too serious so they had to leave quickly leaving valuable loot behind. You are the second wave of agents called to help Manhattn. It is your job to take the call and take Manhattan back. The question is. Will you take the call?</h3>
